** {{ill|Beppu Hatto Onsen Dō|ja|別府八湯温泉道|qq=draft|qq=draft}}: Visitors can try 88 different baths, including these communal ones and day-use baths at ryokan, aiming for recognition as a “Hot Spring Master.”

